data.description: Stunning Home Located in an Upscale and Gated Community. Large Cul-de-Sac Lot, Beautiful Custom Front and Back Iron Doors with Custom Framing, Plantation Shutters Throughout the Home, Custom Closets in Main Bedroom, Large Ceiling Fan in Family Room, Upgraded Chandelier in Foyer, Island Kitchen, Stainless Steel Appliances, Granite Counter Tops, Cathedral Ceilings, Stone Fireplace, Media Room, Large Covered Patio, Large Main Bedroom with Tray Ceiling with Crown molding, Rod Iron Staircase with Upgraded Wood Flooring, One of the Biggest Lots in the community has endless opportunities, Enough Space to put a Pool, Move the Fence to make your own Sports Court and Enjoy Outdoor Space with this large Lot. Almost a half an acre (.46 of an Acre). 3 Car Tandem Garage. Water Softener. Built-in Overhead Storage in the Garage. Two Built-out Attic Storage in the 2nd Story. Security System with Touch Screen Pad. Significant Privacy due to large lot size. Enjoy Crape Myrtle's in the backyard and side yard. The upgraded Elevation features a beautiful combination of Stone and Brick and a Covered Front Area to sit down and enjoy the afternoon. The home features an Upgraded Large Laundry with a Sink and plenty of counter space with cabinets. Luxury Style kitchen abounds with an array of cabinets to fit just about everything a kitchen needs. There are ample cabinets to accommodate large appliances and medium and small cabinets. Come and Admire the Custom Iron Doors they push to close and open (no turning knobs). The fine quality of the finish is noticed in how well-balanced the doors pivot with ease. The plantation shutters match the flooring and the home perfectly, and they do a fantastic job of closing out the light or letting it in. Large Windows in the Main living make the best use of the cathedral-size ceilings. The rest of the home's layout complements the large cathedral ceilings perfectly. The house feels just right when it comes to the home's design. The backyard has a large covered patio. You can feel the privacy and large size when you walk outside. The house inside feels almost new because it is so well taken care of. The Main Bedroom downstairs is Spacious with Upgraded Wood Flooring. The Master Bath Features Iron Framing around the window. Large size Shower and Tub. Framing around the Master Bath mirrors. His and Hers Vanity also has His and Hers Closets. The closets feature Upgraded Shelving and Storage to fit many of your closet needs. There is so much to Love with this home. It takes a visit to appreciate all this home truly has to offer
